{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "33ae5090-481d-4ced-ab0e-02e382d77559", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/33ae5090-481d-4ced-ab0e-02e382d77559@3.pkg/1772602027873/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602028802", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/33ae5090-481d-4ced-ab0e-02e382d77559@3.pkg/1772602027873/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602028802"}, "identifier": "33ae5090-481d-4ced-ab0e-02e382d77559", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>选项A</p>\n\n<p>“教学相长”：出自《虽有嘉肴》，意思是教与学互相促进，其中“长”是“推动、促进”的意思 。</p>\n\n<p>“草长莺飞”：描绘春天里草木生长、黄莺飞舞的景象，这里“长”是“生长”的意思 。&nbsp;二者“长”字含义不同。</p>\n\n<p>选项B</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;“虽有至道”：出自《虽有嘉肴》，指虽然有最好的道理，“至”是“最好的”意思 。</p>\n\n<p>“如获至宝”：好像得到极珍贵的宝物，形容对所得到的东西非常珍视喜爱，“至”同样是“最好的”意思 。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;二者“至”字含义相同。</p>\n\n<p>选项C</p>\n\n<p>“然后能自反也”：出自《虽有嘉肴》，即这样以后才能自我反思，“反”是“反思”的意思 。</p>\n\n<p>“举一反三”：从一件事物的情况、道理类推而知道许多事物的情况、道理，形容善于类推，能由此及彼，“反”是“类推”的意思 。</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;二者“反”字含义不同。</p>\n\n<p>选项D</p>\n\n<p>“然后能自强也”：出自《虽有嘉肴》，意为这样以后才能自我勉励，“强”是“勉励”的意思 。</p>\n\n<p>“身强力壮”：形容身体强壮有力，“强”是“强壮”的意思 。&nbsp;二者“强”字含义不同。</p>\n\n<p>综上，答案是B，因为只有B选项中划线字“至”的含义相同，都为“最好的”意思 。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">3.下列加点词意思相同的一项是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "3.下列加点词意思相同的一项是（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/33ae5090-481d-4ced-ab0e-02e382d77559@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754293322191", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:11.9500pt;\">教学相<span class=\"dot\">长 </span>草长莺<span class=\"dot\">飞</span></p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:11.9500pt;\">虽有<span class=\"dot\">至</span>道 如获<span class=\"dot\">至​</span>​宝</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:11.9500pt;\">然后能自<span class=\"dot\">反</span>也 举一<span class=\"dot\">反</span>三</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:11.9500pt;\">然后能自<span class=\"dot\">强</span>也 身<span class=\"dot\">强</span>力壮</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:12.0000pt;\">3.下列加点词意思相同的一项是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "ff8080814371757b014390fcdce504bd", "5136342960", "44bec6